title: FHM India - May 2016 (gnv64)
description:
FHM India - May 2016
English | 100 pages | True PDF | 29.9 mb

FHM India - India's most talked about men's magazine as well as the world's largest men's lifestyle magazine which boasts of a strong, socially relevant, irreverent editorial. A magazine featuring edgy, fast paced writing; with tips and tricks and everything else a new man needs. It showcases reviews and previews of Video Games, Gadgets, Cars, Nightlife, Sports, Food, Alcohol, Cinema and Music. The magazine is not only known for its photo shoots with female celebrities but it also ensures strong and varied feature articles. 

Why settle for one when you can double the stakes! The current issue of FHM features two phenomenal covers with two Indian celebs, Radhika Apte and Sunny Leone, standing at disparate ends of what defines beauty in India. Call them the songs of ice and fire. Check out FHM superhero awards as we accord accolades to the most popular faces of 2016. Leave on a food trail with one of the most ingenuous TV presenters, Bob Blumer. And of course, more skin than you can handle...
